description:
玄铁重剑：重剑无锋，大巧不工。请实现一个 Sword 类：

```python
class Sword:
    def __init__(self, name, weight):
        self.name = name
        self.weight = weight

    def __str__(self):
        return f'{self.name}({self.weight}斤)'

    def __repr__(self):
        return f'Sword({self.name!r}, {self.weight})'
```

创建 `Sword('玄铁重剑', 88)` 并 print 它。

输出：`玄铁重剑(88斤)`

